---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center pt-32 pb-24 px-10 max-md:pt-28 max-md:pb-16 max-md:px-6 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Red radial glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute -top-[20%] -right-[10%] w-[70vw] h-[70vw] bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(200,16,46,0.06)_0%,transparent_65%)] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom red line -->
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-[linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(200,16,46,0.2),transparent)]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto w-full relative">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left column: headline + CTA -->
      <div>
        <div
          class="font-display text-[0.75rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-red mb-8 flex items-center gap-4"
        >
          <span class="block w-8 h-px bg-red"></span>
          AI Strategy & Transformation
        </div>

        <h1
          class="font-display text-[clamp(2.8rem,6.5vw,5.5rem)] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-[640px] mb-8"
        >
          Your business doesn't need an AI vendor. It needs to <span class="text-red"
            >become</span
          > one.
        </h1>

        <p
          class="font-serif text-[clamp(1.15rem,2vw,1.4rem)] leading-relaxed text-cream-muted max-w-[540px] mb-12"
        >
          The cost of building custom software has collapsed. What took a dev team
          and six figures now takes weeks and costs almost nothing. Every business
          you compete with will figure this out eventually. The ones that figure it
          out first don't just get ahead â€” they rewrite the rules.
        </p>

        <a
          href="#review"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-red text-cream py-4 px-8 font-display font-bold text-[0.9rem] tracking-[0.06em] uppercase no-underline rounded-sm hover:bg-red-glow hover:shadow-[0_4px_40px_rgba(200,16,46,0.3)] hover:-translate-y-px transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
          Take the AI Possibilities Review
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-[18px] h-[18px] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: AI terminal/dashboard visual -->
      <div class="hidden md:block">
        <div class="terminal-card bg-surface border border-cream/[0.06] rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Terminal header -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-cream/[0.06] bg-surface-2/50">
            <span class="w-[10px] h-[10px] rounded-full bg-[#C8102E]"></span>
            <span class="w-[10px] h-[10px] rounded-full bg-[#E5A000]"></span>
            <span class="w-[10px] h-[10px] rounded-full bg-[#2EA043]"></span>
            <span class="ml-3 font-body text-[0.7rem] text-cream-dim tracking-wide">ai-agent.rs</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Terminal body -->
          <div class="p-5 space-y-3 font-mono text-[0.8rem]">
            <!-- Line 1: keyword + value -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red font-semibold">use</span>
              <span class="text-cream-dim">sovereign::core::agent;</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Line 2: keyword + value -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red font-semibold">use</span>
              <span class="text-cream-dim">sovereign::llm::pipeline;</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Blank line spacer -->
            <div class="h-2"></div>

            <!-- Line 3: function signature -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-red font-semibold">fn</span>
              <span class="text-cream/80">deploy_agent</span>
              <span class="text-cream-dim">() -> Result&lt;()&gt; &#123;</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Code bars (simulated indented code) -->
            <div class="pl-5 space-y-2">
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-red/20" style="width: 65%"></div>
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-cream/10" style="width: 45%"></div>
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-red/15" style="width: 55%"></div>
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-cream/10" style="width: 30%"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Line: inline code -->
            <div class="pl-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-cream-dim">agent.</span><span class="text-red">optimize</span><span class="text-cream-dim">(config)?;</span>
            </div>

            <!-- More code bars -->
            <div class="pl-5 space-y-2">
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-cream/10" style="width: 40%"></div>
              <div class="h-[6px] rounded-full bg-red/20" style="width: 60%"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Closing brace -->
            <div class="text-cream-dim">&#125;</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Status bar -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 border-t border-cream/[0.06] bg-surface-2/30">
            <span class="w-[7px] h-[7px] rounded-full bg-[#2EA043] status-pulse"></span>
            <span class="font-body text-[0.7rem] text-cream-dim tracking-wide">Agent running...</span>
            <span class="ml-auto font-body text-[0.65rem] text-cream-dim/50">v0.4.2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes pulse-glow {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(200, 16, 46, 0.08), 0 0 60px rgba(200, 16, 46, 0.04);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(200, 16, 46, 0.14), 0 0 80px rgba(200, 16, 46, 0.07);
    }
  }

  @keyframes status-blink {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.4;
    }
  }

  .terminal-card {
    animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .status-pulse {
    animation: status-blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
